      "instruction": "Fill a saucepan with water so the chicken breast will be well submerged with at least 2\" / 5cm of water above it."
    },
    {
      "order": 3,
      "instruction": "Bring water to boil. Place chicken breast in water, place lid on, bring back up to the boil. Remove saucepan from stove and set aside for 20 minutes (it's fine up to 45 min, won't overcook)."
